BEY
v.
RASAWEHR 2019-0295 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 15, 2019 Appeal accepted on appellant's proposition of law No. II. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY and STEWART, JJ., dissent.

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW
